fields.name: Required flights of stairs
fields.formula: if((lookup('Moving from','Has elevator') = true),0,(lookup('Moving from', 'Flights of stairs'))) + if((lookup('Moving to','Has elevator') = true),0,(lookup('Moving to', 'Flights of stairs')))

fields.name: Workers still needed
fields.formula: field('Number of movers required') - count(field('Workers assigned'))
